{"id":"2576121875","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2576121875","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjU3NjEyMTg3NQ==","status":"current","title":"Registro de horas en Kubrick","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"Agustin Llado","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Agustin Llado","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"en_GB","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918"}},"when":"2023-11-29T14:46:08.574Z","friendlyWhen":"Nov 29, 2023","message":"","number":7,"minorEdit":false,"syncRev":"8.confluence$content$2576121875.7","syncRevSource":"synchrony-ack","ncsStepVersion":"403","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$2576121875.42","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/2576121875"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2576121875/version/7"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2260140085","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2260140085","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI2MDE0MDA4NQ==","status":"current","title":"Management","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":504478064},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2260140085","tinyui":"/x/NQC3hg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2260140085","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2260140085/Management","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2260140085"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>El registro de las horas en Kubrick desempe&ntilde;a un papel de vital importancia en la gesti&oacute;n de nuestro equipo. De manera semanal, el equipo de gesti&oacute;n compila un informe que recopila las horas trabajadas por todo el equipo para su posterior env&iacute;o al cliente. Por consiguiente, resulta <strong>esencial</strong> que todas las horas trabajadas est&eacute;n debidamente registradas al finalizar la semana.</p><p>Al registrar las horas dedicadas a las tareas asignadas, se recomienda encarecidamente llevar un registro simult&aacute;neo y en tiempo real dentro de Kubrick. Esta pr&aacute;ctica no solo evita la acumulaci&oacute;n de horas para su registro en el &uacute;ltimo d&iacute;a de la semana, sino que tambi&eacute;n contribuye a generar informes m&aacute;s precisos acerca del uso del tiempo invertido en cada tarea. Esto, a su vez, facilita el an&aacute;lisis y asegura la exactitud de los informes.</p><p>El registro de las horas debe ser realizado en ingl&eacute;s.</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1024\" ac:original-width=\"1792\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"760\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231122-203400.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /><h2>Descripci&oacute;n</h2><p>En el caso de estar trabajando en un ticket de Jira, el formato adecuado para la descripci&oacute;n es el siguiente: <code>[ID] - Descripci&oacute;n de la tarea</code>. En el caso de tratarse de una tarea que no cuenta con un ticket en Jira (como las dailies o la generaci&oacute;n de documentaci&oacute;n para el equipo), el formato adecuado ser&aacute; el siguiente: <code>[General] - Descripci&oacute;n de la tarea</code>.</p><h2>Proyecto</h2><p>Cada registro debe estar vinculado al proyecto correspondiente. Si en alg&uacute;n caso no est&aacute; claro a qu&eacute; proyecto debe asociarse una entrada, se recomienda consultar con el PM.</p><p>En lo que respecta a las reuniones e instancias <strong>grupales</strong> que no puedan ser atribuidas a un proyecto espec&iacute;fico, se utilizar&aacute; el proyecto denominado: <code>Team Activities [Internal Syncs, 1:1, Team Issues]</code>, que se encuentra dentro del cliente <code>Bancard</code>.</p><ac:image ac:align=\"left\" ac:layout=\"align-start\" ac:original-height=\"48\" ac:original-width=\"290\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230830-223709.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p><em>Es importante tener en cuenta que existe un proyecto con dicho nombre para todos los clientes de Qubika.</em></p><h2>Tag</h2><p>El uso de tags es obligatorio y debe reflejar el tipo de tarea realizada. Los tags disponibles son los siguientes:</p><ac:image ac:align=\"left\" ac:layout=\"align-start\" ac:original-height=\"317\" ac:original-width=\"299\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230830-223612.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>Una gu&iacute;a para los casos mas comunes es la siguiente:</p><ul><li><p>Desarrollo: <code>Development</code></p></li><li><p>QA de una feature: <code>QA</code></p></li><li><p>Correcci&oacute;n de feature o bug: <code>Development (bug)</code></p></li><li><p>Code Review: <code>Development (Code Review)</code></p></li><li><p>Reunion, videollamada, huddle: <code>Communication/Management</code></p></li></ul><h2>Ejemplos</h2><h3>Desarrollo</h3><p><code>[General] - Descripci&oacute;n de la tarea</code></p><ac:image ac:align=\"left\" ac:layout=\"align-start\" ac:original-height=\"171\" ac:original-width=\"226\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230417-115332.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>En este caso el registro seria:</p><p><code>[PCEPA-46] - Search filter by service</code></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"63\" ac:original-width=\"1505\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230830-224325.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><h3>Reunion / Videollamada / Huddle</h3><p><code>[General] - Nombre de reunion</code></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"62\" ac:original-width=\"1510\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230830-223105.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><h3>Tarea sin ticket</h3><p><code>[General] - Descripci&oacute;n de la tarea</code></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"63\" ac:original-width=\"1502\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230830-224109.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><hr /><p><em>Este fue el &uacute;ltimo paso del M&oacute;dulo 1 del Onboarding de <strong>Bancard</strong>. Muchas gracias por el inter&eacute;s y tiempo dedicado en &eacute;l. </em></p><p><em>Siguiente M&oacute;dulo</em> &rarr; </p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"block\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Proceso de Desarrollo\" ri:version-at-save=\"6\" /><ac:link-body>Proceso de Desarrollo</ac:link-body></ac:link><p> </p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2576121875"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":924},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2576121875/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2576121875/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2576121875/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2576121875/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2576121875","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2576121875/Registro+de+horas+en+Kubrick","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2576121875","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2576121875","tinyui":"/x/E4CMmQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}